data.description: Sitting in a quiet cul de sac and backing up to an oak filled greenbelt, it's hard to find a more serene setting to spend time with friends and family.  Natural light pours through this open and spacious home.  Beautiful coffered ceilings tower to 13' in some rooms.  Gourmet kitchen with gas stove, ample prep space on the granite countertops and island, and tons of storage in the beautifully finished cabinets, make this an entertainers dream.  Game room and home office are and added bonus.  Situated in the prestigious Vintage Oaks neighborhood, you will enjoy resort-style amenities including the new 7,000 sq. ft. fitness club.
